&lt;p&gt;The StaffBank for Epsom and St Helier are seeking enthusiastic Nurses to work with our fantastic Community Night Nursing team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Working bank is the ultimate in flexibility, without compromising your career. We are looking to recruit qualified community nurses with experience who are looking to work night shifts in our community easily accessible from London and the surrounding area and working as part of the Night nursing team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;To join, you must:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Currently be registered with the NMC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Be eligible to work in the UK&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Pass an enhanced DBS check&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;* Have a minimum of 6 months relevant experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We offer great rates, access to the NHS pension, free mandatory training and the support of a professional and friendly team from the moment you register with us, to your first shift and beyond.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Apply now to join the StaffBank team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Bank Partners are a leading provider of independent staffing bank management and outsourced staffing services providing workers to some of the largest trusts in the NHS. We have over 20 years’ experience in managing hospital banks and we take pride in the knowledge that we provide a high quality service to the trusts we represent, supplying them with workers across multiple specialism’s including Doctors, Nurses and Allied Health Professionals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
